claims:
10. A computer system, comprising: 
a database containing data records associating a plurality of medical risks and a plurality of health parameters; and  a processor configured to: 
obtain data records associated with one or more health variables and a plurality of medical risks from a plurality of MRS models based on an expert knowledge combination process; 
establish a medical risk process model indicative of interrelationships between the plurality of medical risks and a plurality of health parameters based on the data records; 
obtain a set of values corresponding to the plurality of health parameters; 
calculate values of the plurality of medical risks simultaneously based upon the set of values corresponding to the plurality of health parameters and the medical risk process model; 
optimize the plurality of health parameters to minimize the plurality of medical risks simultaneously; and 
present the values of the plurality of medical risks.
